column5: Anybody fish south narrows just north of Nestor falls ? How is it ?

Here's a report from somebody who fished it. (Look at his report from June 7). Sounds like a good smallmouth bass lake. You could talk to Paul at Muskie Bay Resort and he might be able to give you more info as well....http://fishcatchingtravel.com/2016/0...ke-6716/#more-'
